Burna boy and Stefflon Don British rapper, Stefflon Don’s has revealed that she and Burna Boy will be getting married for sure as she calls him her husband during her interview on Beat 1. The rapper during the interview stated that she’s very sure she and Boy will get married. When asked ‘what’s the situation with you and Burna?’ she replied with; Oh my gosh, that’s my husband… we are gonna get married…and make babies… He’s amazing. On how they met each other, Stefflon Don revealed they met in Ghana, her happiness while divulging details, radiating all over.  "Burna is my husband …" – Stefflon Don  This is really sweet #Burna #stefflondon #Notjustok A post shared by  Notjustok.com (@notjustok) on Jun 14, 2019 at 11:47am PDT //www.instagram.com/embed.js Burna Boy has mentioned as his ‘Wifey’ more than once but while we thought it was just a way to call her his woman, Stefflon Don’s proclamation is telling us this is serious than we thought. The post ‘Burna Is My Husband…” – Stefflon Don appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: Not just okay